weaponDirection 
Behavior: global 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Returns the direction that the vehicle weapon is aiming in. 
For addons the weapon name must be an entry in CfgWeapons. 
Returns an array in format [x, z, y]  
Syntax:  
 vehicleName weaponDirection weaponName 
Parameters: 
vehicleName: Object 
weaponName: String 
Return Value: 
 Array - format Vector3D